column5: A couple pics to share.              Cheers.
thats a pretty pretty fish
You seem to have em dialed in! Great lookin Steel  Clarence
Nice fish.  Didn't you very recently have a different board name?
i was thinking the same thing.... lol
A name can make you or break you in life. Nice post and a much better choice on a name.   I imagine you are a gamer as well as a good fisherman.   Thanks   Art
Just how does a name make you or break you in life?    Nice fish bro
Nice fish bro, save some for me, see you out there!
sixaxis?  never heard of that strain.

Yeah, I had to change my name because it was inappropriate... crappy because I had the name since 07 lol....I dont think a name on a board will have any influence on life.I personally liked the other name better. Didn't really have a choice though. Thx for the comments!
LOL!
Great fish. It must have been nice weather to be fishing in a t-shirt!  Good thing I didn't use my favorite Jimi Hendrix song as my screen name.
Nice fish/pics.
I prefer Z-axis  Nice fish
siaxis? Is that what they call it on the streets now?  Nice fish
As a great man once said to me  " If you're a tailor and your name is Hitler..there's a good chance you'll never find a job in the schmata industry.    Art
Nice work!
Personally I think it's a reflection of society for judging names and not people, but whatever.

I don't think the name would have been a big deal...  But at the end of his posts he was making reference to a substance that isn't "family" friendly...  So I can see how the image he was putting out there wasn't right for this "family" site...   Sweet fishing man...  Can't wait to get my first steelhead on a float...
Fantastic
Your eyes look all squinty and closed in them pics...LMAO  Nice fish.
